{"tid":1346902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有記者睇緊連登，希望你地幫手跟一跟上環嗰邊嘅消息","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:06:54.000Z","uid":89185,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"c3dff3a0fa839d9756211cd74150433cf43a894c","tid":1346902,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"我岩岩碌立場，差唔多全部都係講緊元朗嗰邊，上環嗰邊無咩新聞。<br />\n求吓記者們幫手跟一跟上環嗰邊嘅消息好嗎？<br />\n香港人兩邊嘅消息都需要知，兩邊都要跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果你地都畀港共轉移哂視線嘅話，上環嗰邊所有人，包括和理非同前線搏命嘅戰友都會變哂condom仔架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求吓你地幫吓我地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb35f3c8b96aa142a7847071faeddb98aef92c8e","tid":1346902,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"推到畀記者們見到幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201e5a059440ee65782d51d84be148049a9110f2","tid":1346902,"uid":39492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"請廣傳!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsOPaYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsOPaYx.jpg&h=02945277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L7EyCDx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7EyCDx.jpg&h=e011f168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meREybS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeREybS.jpg&h=a97aa08c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEvYOLc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEvYOLc.jpg&h=c1d74bb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba2b6deab2dd8aa94ef87311cb8c53adb5e496bf","tid":1346902,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 係時候組織起嚟<br />\n守衛香港 保護香港人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以武制暴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>香港防衛隊由保安公司做起<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344373\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n琴晚兩大焦點<br />\n<br />\n1. 上環無預警地開槍企圖殺害市民，令人群，記者恐慌及受傷！<br />\n<br />\n2. 國家恐怖組織喺元朗入侵西鐵站暴打市民，警方以無武器或合法集結放過恐怖組織。"},{"pid":"8b139b1c39a1846b64e9337132d0f00f1b647e0c","tid":1346902,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"支持, 好想知琴晚上環咩事. <br />\n兩邊都係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30ded71252b2b9e500f44dcb8e94170c22a375f","tid":1346902,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2295553343620f555886fe30263a70f26bd1e6c","tid":1346902,"uid":284624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"文宣三件事<br />\n1. 中環警犬無預警瞄頭開槍，請話比外國記者朋友知<br />\n2. 元朗牛屎佬打人，警黑合作，請話比街坊鄰里知<br />\n3. 噴黑中聯辦國徽，推翻共產政權，請話比全世界知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醒喇香港人</span>"},{"pid":"ce880d3ac039c1023d04f4b931539f767a1fbfb1","tid":1346902,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"急！係咪有人中槍?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342536</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69a8c47070a28ee817255c306aeba368e1690518","tid":1346902,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"依家唔係我地唔想理上環嗰邊，而係完全唔夠資訊呀！<br />\n求吓記者們幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e90939e5ecd765adfacb567e1764db504d117ae","tid":1346902,"uid":84657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"cc77d24e8f2aa92d05625d2e5eb89292e448a332","tid":1346902,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"尋日上環d手足唔係12點咁上下撤退晒咩？"},{"pid":"f9e71664ae61e479c2a078673aabc73ab0652223","tid":1346902,"uid":268086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbffe4090af4e391a5c5641061e03f7a13228c0","tid":1346902,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77fa3a45ba0e77048fbe8a103fbe22dd881754e","tid":1346902,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"淨係想佢地報個平安姐！<br />\n<br />\n人就應該拉唔到，但受傷嘅有冇醫療呀"},{"pid":"b69effe5c92c64c5c7aa2ccea6c0424af666b8e8","tid":1346902,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"上環果邊好似真係無乜聲氣<br />\n唔知係因為真係無傷亡 / 無人俾狗拉定點"},{"pid":"3aca3fbb90205c5538c49b9c5b308b92fcda4db2","tid":1346902,"uid":123677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n一定要跟埋上環